  <brief_title>Functional and Morphologic Aspects of Intravitreal Triamcinolone for Uveitis-associated Cystoid Macular Edema</brief_title>
  <official_title>Functional and Morphologic Aspects of Intravitreal Triamcinolone for Uveitis-associated Cystoid Macular Edema</official_title>
  <sponsors>
